des:
Viral Launch Market Intelligence leverages a complex and intricate algorithm designed to help you avoid money wasting products and source only money making home runs. The tool analyzes incredible amounts of real time and historical data to produce critical stats, draw strategic correlations, and define pivotal trends.

If our system rates your next product idea as 5 stars, you’ve found a gold mine. If your next product idea is 3 stars or less, you can thank us for helping save you from wasting thousands of dollars on sourcing a bad product.
